OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: Calls to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbring benefit and pension  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frises forward              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers are facing growing calls to  
OL,6, bring forward large increases in       
OL,7, benefits and the state pension which   
OL,8, will be paid from next April.          
OL,10,FCharities want benefits to increase now
OL,11,Fto help people struggling with the cost
OL,12,Fof living, particularly energy bills.  
OL,14,FA well-established system means the    
OL,15,Fannual increase in benefits will match 
OL,16,Fthis September's inflation rate - but  
OL,17,Fwill only be paid from April 2023.     
OL,19,FThe Treasury says there are technical  
OL,20,Fconstraints in making earlier payments.
